This project is based on work from the GitHub repository "pocesar/actor-shopify-scraper" by Paulo Cesar.

Original repository: https://github.com/pocesar/actor-shopify-scraper
Original author: Paulo Cesar

Modifications include:
- Migration to Storefront GraphQL with per-host batching
- Sitemap lastmod filtering and incremental processing
- Buffered dataset writes and performance improvements
- Code refactoring, naming, and structure changes

